<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="news-n">news <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /njuːz/    美 /nuːz/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>新闻；消息：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a <strong>piece of news</strong> 
一条新闻</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>the latest news</strong> (<strong>about / on / of</strong>)
(关于…的) 最新消息</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>No news is good news</strong>. 
没有消息就是好消息。</p></div></div>